I never even said it.

28
00:03:06,043 --> 00:03:08,511
You should make love
on the beach all by yourself.

29
00:03:08,612 --> 00:03:13,345
- It would be wonderful. I mean it.
- But?

30
00:03:14,785 --> 00:03:17,083
[Sighs]
That there...

31
00:03:17,187 --> 00:03:22,454
