not knowing what to do with yourself.

49
00:04:27,524 --> 00:04:31,460
- Believe me, I've been there.
- And what do you know of it?

50
00:04:31,562 --> 00:04:35,726
Long and fascinating tale.
Ghost story, in fact.

51
00:04:35,833 --> 00:04:38,233
