58
00:04:59,623 --> 00:05:02,285
Yeah. Well, I'm afraid
that never goes away.

59
00:05:02,393 --> 00:05:05,191
Anyhow, I though Wesley
was giving you a primer on all things human.

60
00:05:05,295 --> 00:05:07,263
He and I are no longer
having intercourse.

61
00:05:07,364 --> 00:05:09,332
Yeah. L...
You what? What?

62
00:05:09,433 --> 00:05:11,765
He has ceased
communication with me.

63
00:05:11,869 --> 00:05:14,303
Oh. Oh.
Communi...

64
00:05:14,405 --> 00:05:18,432
My recent reversion
to the Burkle persona disturbed him...

65
00:05:18,542 --> 00:05:20,510
and he will not
tell me why.

66
00:05:21,745 --> 00:05:23,713
You don't know?

67
00:05:23,814 --> 00:05:27,807
You may not think you're as powerful
as you were, Highness...

68
00:05:27,918 --> 00:05:32,946
but looking like Fred,
for some of us...

69
00:05:33,057 --> 00:05:35,287
