71
00:05:40,931 --> 00:05:43,331
<i>Ah. And there's</i>
<i>the man himself.</i>

72
00:05:43,434 --> 00:05:45,834
<i>Angel, I'd like you to meet</i>
<i>Senator Brucker.</i>

73
00:05:45,936 --> 00:05:48,336
Senator. Welcome
to Wolfram and Hart.

74
00:05:48,439 --> 00:05:51,499
I go way back with this firm.
Back when Holland Manners was in charge.

75
00:05:51,608 --> 00:05:53,701
You'll find things
have changed a bit since then.

76
00:05:53,811 --> 00:05:56,575
- Charles Gunn.
- Head of our Legal Department.

77
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:59,547
- Oh. And this is Ernesto, my personal...
- Vampire.

78
00:05:59,650 --> 00:06:03,051
Aide. I always forget your kind
can sense each other.

79
00:06:03,153 --> 00:06:05,621
<i>Well, I believe in</i>
<i>diversity on my staff.</i>

80
00:06:05,723 --> 00:06:08,692
- It was a big part of my campaign.
- How commendable.

81
00:06:08,792 --> 00:06:12,319
- Harmony, you mind gettin' us some coffee?
- Coming up.

82
00:06:12,429 --> 00:06:14,727
Oh. Thank you, no.
No coffee.

83
00:06:14,832 --> 00:06:17,596
But if it isn't any trouble,
I think Ernesto might like some blood.

84
00:06:17,701 --> 00:06:19,692
Virgin, if you have it.
Room temperature's fine.

85
00:06:19,803 --> 00:06:22,704
<i>Sorry. We have</i>
<i>a "no human blood"policy.</i>

86
00:06:22,806 --> 00:06:27,334
I can offer you something in a rodent.
We have some fruity, unassuming vole...

87
00:06:27,444 --> 00:06:31,710
<i>I think we could make an exception</i>
<i>to our policy this time for the senator.</i>

88
00:06:31,815 --> 00:06:33,840
Couldn't we, Angel?

89
00:06:33,951 --> 00:06:36,215
Harmony, the lab might have something
in the blood bank.

90
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:39,721
<i>- Why don't you go check it out?</i>
<i>- Okay. You're the boss, boss.</i>

91
00:06:41,458 --> 00:06:43,722
Could I maybe
just have a teeny-weeny...

92
00:06:43,827 --> 00:06:46,352
- No.
- Just thought I'd ask.

93
00:06:46,463 --> 00:06:50,422
Well, Senator, if there's anything you need,
please call on me.

94
00:06:50,534 --> 00:06:52,695
Rest assured,
you're in good hands.

95
00:06:52,803 --> 00:06:55,033
Shall we?

96
00:06:56,974 --> 00:07:01,434
<i>- Angel. There's been another fatality in Funville.</i>
- What?

97
00:07:01,545 --> 00:07:05,208
