when you guys get through.

136
00:09:06,970 --> 00:09:09,165
- Pardon me?
<i>- Help convince Conley he is.</i>

137
00:09:09,273 --> 00:09:12,868
You've got some sort of brainwashing
capabilities here, don't you?

138
00:09:12,976 --> 00:09:15,069
