of the Fell Brethren?

158
00:10:36,393 --> 00:10:38,361
Right.
How is Ed?

159
00:10:38,462 --> 00:10:40,987
You know the Fells.
All they can talk about is the baby.

160
00:10:41,098 --> 00:10:43,658
"The baby's doin' this now."
"The baby's doin' that."

161
00:10:43,767 --> 00:10:46,600
<i>"What a wonderful ritual sacrifiiice he'll make."</i>
