enough nice things about you.

163
00:10:49,106 --> 00:10:51,802
- Oh, great.
- Hey, you're really comin' through, big guy.

164
00:10:51,908 --> 00:10:55,969
- There's a real buzz about you.
- So, how much longer do I
have to wait for an answer?

165
00:10:56,079 --> 00:10:59,606
Hey, these things take time.
Trust me. It won't be long now.

166
00:11:06,356 --> 00:11:09,154
See? This isn't so bad now.

167
00:11:10,594 --> 00:11:14,223
Little field trip
out in the...

168
00:11:14,331 --> 00:11:16,822
well, what passes
in this city for fresh air.

169
00:11:18,235 --> 00:11:21,204
All we need now is to bag ourselves
a Boretz demon...

170
00:11:21,304 --> 00:11:23,795
we got ourselves
a perfect date.

171
00:11:23,907 --> 00:11:25,898
[Illyria]
Angel does not think...

172
00:11:26,009 --> 00:11:29,501
