[Sighs]

190
00:12:29,206 --> 00:12:32,300
Not that I don't think the sod could end up
being a megalomaniacal bastard...

191
00:12:32,409 --> 00:12:35,139
it's just if he did,
I'd know it.

192
00:12:36,246 --> 00:12:38,214
I'd feel it.

193
00:12:38,315 --> 00:12:40,476
[Illyria]
You'll have proof soon enough.

194
00:12:40,584 --> 00:12:43,018
A corrupted ruler
on such a path...

195
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:45,953
sees treachery and betrayal
all around him.

196
00:12:46,056 --> 00:12:49,924
He cannot suffer intimates.
He will eventually turn against them.

197
00:12:50,026 --> 00:12:52,324
[Chuckles]
Guess I don't have to worry about that...

198
00:12:52,429 --> 00:12:54,989
'cause Angel and me
have never been intimate.

199
00:12:55,098 --> 00:12:57,828
- Except that one...
- Mark me.

200
00:12:57,934 --> 00:12:59,902
He will murder
one of you.

201
00:13:00,003 --> 00:13:02,164
<i>Actually...</i>

202
00:13:02,272 --> 00:13:04,570
he already has.

203
00:13:04,674 --> 00:13:07,006
